page.title: 14My Day (1)
page.content: A day in my life I am Jonathan Smith.Ilive at 9 Ronald shay Close.I get up at 7 o,clock,have my breakfast then get washed and dress ed.I leave home.At 9.00 we go into our lessons followed by maths.After break we have English.At twelve we have our dinner.After dinner we play out until five past one.We then work until two twenty,play again and go home at three thirty five.When I get home I change and switch on the t.v.After tea I sometimes go to Stuart Lloyds house.I come back at eight.I have a coffee and watch t.v until nine twenty then I go to bed.
